T02D3693:327a-3: 'phags ma sgrol ma la bstod pa /
T02D3693:327a-4: bcom ldan 'das ngag gi dbang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327a-5: dad pa'i lteng ka rab tu rgyas pa la //
T02D3693:327a-6: 'dun pa padma'i rtsa ba rab tu brtan //
T02D3693:327a-7: rtsol ba drag po padma'i gdan la bzhugs //
T02D3693:327a-8: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327a-9: 'gro ba nyon mongs tshad pas gdungs pa la //
T02D3693:327a-10: thugs rjes bsil mdzad zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
T02D3693:327a-11: 'gro ba nyam thag sgrol ba'i lha mo ste //
T02D3693:327a-12: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327a-13: tshogs gnyis shing rta'i 'khor lo lta bu yis //
T02D3693:327a-14: sgrib gnyis bcom nas sa bcur rab gnas te //
T02D3693:327a-15: lha mo'i tshul du 'khor ba ma stongs bzhugs //
T02D3693:327a-16: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327a-17: nyon mongs mi g-yo ri ltar brtan pa'i sku //
T02D3693:327a-18: yon tan rab rdzogs sha lus shin tu rgyas //
T02D3693:327a-19: byams pas thugs g-yos nu 'bur rgyas pa can //
T02D3693:327a-20: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327a-21: 'khor bas mgos sku mdog 'gying bag can //
T02D3693:327a-22: sgeg pa'i cha lugs rin chen rgyan cha can //
T02D3693:327b-0: dbu skra sngo ljang rigs lnga'i @327b cod pan can //
T02D3693:327b-1: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327b-2: zag med bde rgyas zhal ras 'dzum bag can //
T02D3693:327b-3: rnam snang las byung phrin las thugs rje can //
T02D3693:327b-4: bdud 'joms mda' gzhu thabs dang shes rab can //
T02D3693:327b-5: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327b-6: 'jigs pa skyob mdzad phyag g-yas skyabs sbyin tshul //
T02D3693:327b-7: 'gro ba'i yid 'phrog na tshod bcu drug tshul //
T02D3693:327b-8: las kyi rigs tshogs autpal sngon po'i tshul //
T02D3693:327b-9: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327b-10: skye rgas na 'chi'i chu bo bzhi po las //
T02D3693:327b-11: sgrol ba'i gnyen po mkhas pa khyod lags te //
T02D3693:327b-12: byams pa'i gru 'dzin snying rje'i skya ba can //
T02D3693:327b-13: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3693:327b-14: de ltar tshigs su bcad pa brgyad kyis ni //
T02D3693:327b-15: lha mo nyid la dad pas bstod pa las //
T02D3693:327b-16: des ni 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyis //
T02D3693:327b-17: myur du sangs rgyas go 'phang thob par shog / rje btsun ma sgrol ma la bstod pa /
